msgstr "SKILL.md:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:172
msgid "calc.py（提供 ``entrypoint``，进程内执行；CLI 与 entrypoint 共用同一派发）："
msgstr ""
"calc.py, providing ``entrypoint`` for in-process execution; CLI and "
