#: ../../skill_guide.md:231 ../../skill_guide.md:413
msgid "与环境交互"
msgstr "Interact with the environment"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:233
msgid ""
"在 SKILL 正文里说明何时调用内置 **`ask_env`** 工具即可；不要在 frontmatter 里写 "
"``executor``（框架不解析）。"
msgstr ""
"Just state in the SKILL body when to call the built-in **`codegen`** "
"tool; do not write ``executor`` in the frontmatter (the framework will "
"not parse it)."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:235
msgid "最佳实践"
msgstr "Best practices"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:237
msgid "1. 保持单一职责"
msgstr "1. Maintain a single responsibility"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:239
msgid "每个 Skill 只做一件事："
msgstr "Each Skill only does one thing:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:241
msgid "✅ `mood-check`: 只更新当前情绪状态"
msgstr "✅ `mood-check`: updates only current mood state"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:242
msgid "✅ `social-reflection`: 只更新社交关系"
msgstr "✅ `social-reflection`: updates only social relationships"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:243
msgid "❌ `mood_and_plan`: 做太多事情"
msgstr "❌ `needs_and_emotion`: Doing too many things"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:245
msgid "2. 在正文写清产出文件"
msgstr "2. Write the output file clearly in the text"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:247
msgid ""
"在 Markdown 里列出会写入的路径（如 ``state/result.json``）；frontmatter 不解析 "
"``outputs``、``inputs``、``requires`` 等扩展字段。"
msgstr ""
"List the paths that will be written in Markdown (such as "
"``state/result.json``); frontmatter does not parse extension fields such "
"as ``outputs``, ``inputs``, ``requires``, etc."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:249
msgid "3. 处理缺失文件"
msgstr "3. Handle missing files"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:251
msgid "Skill应该优雅处理输入文件不存在的情况："
msgstr ""
"The skill should handle gracefully the case where the input file does not"
