#: ../../skill_guide.md:259
msgid "4. 提供示例"
msgstr "4. Provide examples"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:261
msgid "示例帮助LLM理解预期行为："
msgstr "Examples help LLM understand expected behavior:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:281
msgid "5. 避免冗余描述"
msgstr "5. Avoid redundant descriptions"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:283
msgid "不需要告诉LLM\"仔细思考\"或\"认真分析\"，它会自然地做这些。"
msgstr ""
"There is no need to tell LLM to \"think carefully\" or \"analyze "
"carefully\", it will do this naturally."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:285
msgid "文件结构约定"
msgstr "File structure convention"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:287
msgid "推荐使用以下目录结构："
msgstr "It is recommended to use the following directory structure:"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:300
msgid "调试技巧"
msgstr "Debugging Tips"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:302
msgid "**查看workspace文件**：检查输出文件是否正确生成"
msgstr ""
"**Check workspace files**: Check whether the output file is generated "
"correctly"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:303
msgid "**检查tool_calls.jsonl**：查看LLM调用了哪些工具"
msgstr "**Check tool_calls.jsonl**: Check which tools are called by LLM"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:304
msgid "**简化描述**：如果Skill行为异常，尝试简化描述"
msgstr ""
"**Simplify description**: If the Skill behaves abnormally, try to "
"simplify the description"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:305
msgid "**添加示例**：示例通常能显著改善LLM理解"
msgstr "**Add examples**: Examples often significantly improve LLM understanding"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:307
msgid "示例：完整的Skill"
msgstr "Example: Complete Skill"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:381
msgid "常见问题"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:383
msgid "**Q: Skill之间如何通信？**"
msgstr "**Q: How do Skills communicate with each other?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:385
msgid "A: 通过workspace文件。一个Skill写入文件，另一个Skill读取。"
msgstr ""
"A: Through the workspace file. One Skill writes to the file and another "
"Skill reads."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:387
msgid "**Q: 如何控制Skill执行顺序？**"
msgstr "**Q: How to control Skill execution order?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:389
msgid ""
"A: 由主模型在工具循环里决定先 ``activate_skill`` 哪一个；若有硬依赖，在 SKILL.md 正文写清并引导先激活依赖 "
"skill。"
msgstr ""
"A: The main model decides which ``activate_skill`` to use first in the "
"tool loop; if there is a hard dependency, write it clearly in the "
"SKILL.md text and guide the dependent skill to be activated first."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:391
msgid "**Q: Skill可以调用其他Skill吗？**"
msgstr "**Q: Can a Skill call other Skills?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:393
msgid "A: 不直接调用。通过workspace文件松耦合，LLM决定何时激活哪个Skill。"
msgstr ""
"A: Not called directly. Loosely coupled through workspace files, LLM "
"decides when to activate which Skill."

#: ../../skill_guide.md:395
msgid "**Q: 如何测试Skill？**"
msgstr "**Q: How to test a Skill?**"

#: ../../skill_guide.md:397
msgid "A: 创建测试workspace，放置输入文件，运行agent，检查输出文件。"
msgstr ""
"A: Create a test workspace, place input files, run the agent, and check "
"the output files."

